{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/blog/edwith-boost-course/4","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jin_young Kim","siteUrl":"https://kestrel960408.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>해당 게시물은 [ 부스트코스 ] - 웹프로그래밍 강의( Browser Event, Event object, Event handler )를 기반으로 합니다. </p>\n<h3>Summary</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Event 란</li>\n<li>Event 요소</li>\n<li>Event 사용법</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>What is event?</h3>\n<p> 이벤트란 비주기적 또는 비동기적으로 일어나는 일을 의미합니다. 정리하면, 특정 일이 일어나지만, 그 빈도와 주기는 알 수 없으며, 특정 대상 또는 상황에 일어나는 일을 의미합니다.</p>\n<p> 웹에서는 이벤트는 매우 다양합니다. 예제로</p>\n<ul>\n<li>키보드 또는 마우스 입력</li>\n<li>브라우저의 창 크기 변화</li>\n</ul>\n<p>  등이 이외에 많은 경우가 존재합니다.</p>\n<h3>Event의 요소</h3>\n<p> 이벤트는 크게 3가지의 요소로 구분이 되어집니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>이벤트 발생자 ( Target )\n이벤트가 일어날 객체를 의미합니다. 보통 하나의 Dom elemnet 단위로 지정을 합니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>이벤트 종류 ( Type )\n같은 객체에 대해서, 일어난 이벤트를 의미합니다. 하나의 element에서라도 click, change등이 존재할 수 있습니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>이벤트 발생 시, 행동 ( Handler )\n이벤트가 일어났을 때 일어나는 실행될 함수를 정의합니다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Event 사용하기!</h3>\n<p> 그렇다면 이벤트는 어떻게 사용할까요? 이벤트를 사용하기 위해서는 target 객체에 이벤트를 등록하는 과정이 필요합니다. 크게 두 가지 방법이 존재합니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Event Listner 사용\nevent, handler을 모두 생 후 이를 연결</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">  <span class=\"token comment\">//target 지정</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> elem <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//event 생성</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> event <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'push'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// event 등록</span>\n  elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'push'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'pushed!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// event 발생</span>\n  elem<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dispatchEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  결과 \n  pushed<span class=\"token operator\">!</span>\n  <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>DOM element에 속성으로 추가\n미리 정의되어 있는 리스너에 handler을 등록</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>button<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    Hello?\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/javascript<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//target 지정</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> btn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"button\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token comment\">//event 지정</span>\n    btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hello?'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3d937d684c130b515a2c0ebf4543e51a/47b26/boostCourse-8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 395px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 45.56962025316456%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"boostCourse-8.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3d937d684c130b515a2c0ebf4543e51a/47b26/boostCourse-8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3d937d684c130b515a2c0ebf4543e51a/55fcc/boostCourse-8.png 238w,\n/static/3d937d684c130b515a2c0ebf4543e51a/47b26/boostCourse-8.png 395w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 395px) 100vw, 395px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h5>Event 정리</h5>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bcdae7b5131821e7059da394bd55674f/bf3e8/boostCourse-9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 795px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 41.76100628930818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"boostCourse-9.png\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bcdae7b5131821e7059da394bd55674f/bf3e8/boostCourse-9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bcdae7b5131821e7059da394bd55674f/55fcc/boostCourse-9.png 238w,\n/static/bcdae7b5131821e7059da394bd55674f/02bcc/boostCourse-9.png 475w,\n/static/bcdae7b5131821e7059da394bd55674f/bf3e8/boostCourse-9.png 795w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 795px) 100vw, 795px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>생각해보기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>event type에는 어떤 것들이 있나요? 마우스, 키보드 관련 타입 들을 자세히 알아보세요.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> Mouse Event에는 다양한 값이 존재합니다. 대표적으로</p>\n<ul>\n<li>입력이 들어온 객체</li>\n<li>screen / layout/ page/... 등 상의 위치</li>\n<li>ctrl / alt / shift key, push 여부</li>\n</ul>\n<p>UI에 대한 위치정보, 상호작용할 키의 여부 등등이 존재합니다.</p>\n<p>다음 글에서는 이벤트가 다른 element로 전파되어지는 과정에 대해서 알아보도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<h3>참조</h3>\n<h4>post</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>post 01 : <a href=\"https://webclub.tistory.com/340\">event 란 무엇인가?</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>추가 정보</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>MDN web docs : <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/Guide/Events/Creating_and_triggering_events\">이벤트 생성 및 트리거</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>해당 게시물은 [ 부스트코스 ] - 웹프로그래밍 강의(  Browser Event, Event object, Event handler )를 기반으로 하얐습니다.\n더 자세한 내용에 대해서 알고 싶으시다면, 아래에 안내되는 페이지에서 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>부스트코스 메인 페이지 :  <a href=\"https://www.edwith.org/boostcourse-web\">https://www.edwith.org/boostcourse-web</a>\n이번 포스트와 관련된 페이지 : <a href=\"https://www.edwith.org/boostcourse-web/lecture/16700/\">https://www.edwith.org/boostcourse-web/lecture/16700/</a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4c7b79cfa18897fc278ca25bd6059871/297e2/edwith-nametech.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 491px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 46.23217922606924%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"nametech\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4c7b79cfa18897fc278ca25bd6059871/297e2/edwith-nametech.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4c7b79cfa18897fc278ca25bd6059871/940d7/edwith-nametech.jpg 238w,\n/static/4c7b79cfa18897fc278ca25bd6059871/201e0/edwith-nametech.jpg 475w,\n/static/4c7b79cfa18897fc278ca25bd6059871/297e2/edwith-nametech.jpg 491w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 491px) 100vw, 491px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 14, 2020","path":"/blog/edwith-boost-course/4","tags":"web, edwith-boost-course","title":"[BoostCourse] - Browser Event, Event object, Event handler"}}},"pageContext":{"refPath":"/blog/edwith-boost-course/4","prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"[React] - React의 Hook ","path":"/blog/react/2"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"[BoostCourse] - Ajax 응답 처리와 비동기","path":"/blog/edwith-boost-course/5"}}}}}